==古生態學==
沉重龍來自白堊紀晚期的{{link-en|巴侯巴瑞爾組|Bajo Barreal Formation}}，年代為晚[[森諾曼階|森諾曼階]]至早[[土侖階|土侖階]]。同一地區的其他物種包含[[蛇頸龜科|蛇頸龜科]]的''Bonapartemys''和''Prochelidella''、[[阿貝力龍科|阿貝力龍科]]的[[怪踝龍|怪踝龍]]、一個未鑑定的[[食肉牛龍亞科|食肉牛龍亞科]]、<ref name="martinez2004"/>[[鳥腳類|鳥腳類]]的[[獨孤龍|獨孤龍]]和[[南方稜齒龍|南方稜齒龍]]、泰坦巨龍類的[[德魯斯拉龍|德魯斯拉龍]]、[[似傾齒龍|似傾齒龍]]、[[薩米恩托龍|薩米恩托龍]]、[[虛骨龍類|虛骨龍類]]的[[安尼柯龍|安尼柯龍]]。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Martínez|first=Rubén D. F.|last2=Lamanna|first2=Matthew C.|last3=Novas|first3=Fernando E.|last4=Ridgely|first4=Ryan C.|last5=Casal|first5=Gabriel A.|last6=Martínez|first6=Javier E.|last7=Vita|first7=Javier R.|last8=Witmer|first8=Lawrence M.|date=26 April 2016|editor-last=Joger|editor-first=Ulrich|title=A Basal Lithostrotian Titanosaur (Dinosauria: Sauropoda) with a Complete Skull: Implications for the Evolution and Paleobiology of Titanosauria|url=https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0151661|journal=[[PLOS_ONE|PLOS ONE]]|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0151661|via=[[PLOS_One|PLOS One]]|pmc=4846048|pmid=27115989|volume=11|page=e0151661|access-date=2022-01-06|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417095102/https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0151661|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="weishampel2004">{{cite book|last=Weishampel|first=D.B. |author2=Dodson, P. |author3=Osmolska, H.|year=2004|title=The Dinosauria (Second ed.)|url=https://archive.org/details/dinosauriandedit00weis|publisher=University of California Press|pages=[https://archive.org/details/dinosauriandedit00weis/page/n318 300]–400|isbn=-0-520-24209-2}}</ref>

